{
  "text": "The phytochemical screenings (Table 2) detected are known to have beneficial importance in medicinal sciences. For instance, flavonoids, steroids, tannins and saponins have been reported for their anti-allergic, anticancer, anti-inflammatory, antimicrobial, antioxidant antifungal and anticancer activities, etc. [CITATION_1] .",
